The paper discusses the design and implementation of task-based quantization for MIMO receivers, which involves signal processing, information theory, and machine learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.IT (Information Theory), followed by cs.SY (Systems and Control), cs.MM (Multimedia), cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
